  line
  line `12 Subs. by Act 7 of 2019, s. 12, for clause (14) (w.e.f. 1-7-2020). [Earlier notified w.e.f. 9-1-2020 followed by 1-4-2020]`
  line
  line `13. Ins. by Act 7 of 2019, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-7-2020). [Earlier notified w.e.f. 9-1-2020 followed by 1-4-2020[`
  line
  line `14. Subs. by s. 12, ibid., for clause (16A) (w.e.f. 1-7-2020). [Earlier notified w.e.f. 9-1-2020 followed by 1-4-2020]`
  line
  line `15. The word "and" omitted by Act 5 of 1906, s. 2.`
  line
  line `16. Clause (c) omitted by s. 2, ibid.`
  line
  line `17. Ins. by Act 43 of 1955, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1956).`
  line
  line `18. The word "and" omitted by Act 18 of 1928, s. 2 and the First Schedule.`
  line
  line `19. Ins. by Act 7 of 2019, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-7-2020). [Earlier notified w.e.f. 9-1-2020 followed by 1-4-2020]`
  line
